      <title>亚洲股市、加密货币暴跌，债券价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-05/asian-stocks-crypto-currencies-plunge-as-bonds-rally-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲股市全线下跌，加密货币暴跌，债券上涨，因市场担心美联储对美国经济放缓的政策支持落后。加菲尔德·雷诺兹在“彭博社：中国秀”中对此进行了更多报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-05/asian-stocks-crypto-currencies-plunge-as-bonds-rally-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 02:18:07 GMT</pubDate>
